Red Agency Ads Tool is a Next.js dashboard for campaign-first Meta Ads analysis. It connects Meta accounts, lets the user choose account, campaign scope, date range, and KPI pack, then turns raw Meta insights into KPI cards, charts, health checks, Verdicts, AI-assisted insight tables, and PDF reports. The source snapshot is from commit `5f84240` (`feat(auth): add Facebook OAuth login`) in `tgen16mgc/redagencyads`.